SAFA, INC.
v.
RELIABLE CREDIT ASSN., INC. 2019-0376 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 29, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appellant's motion to refile the notice of appeal under the proper case numbers and caption denied. Appellee's motion to dismiss denied. O'Connor, C.J., would grant appellee's motion to dismiss.

DeWine and Donnelly, JJ., would grant appellant's motion to refile the notice of appeal under the proper case numbers and caption.
